com.terrapin.emwin.object

Class vtecItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.terrapin.emwin.object.vtecItem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class vtecItem
extends Object
implements Serializable
    The VTEC item conveys severe weather conditions: watches, warnings, etc. The format is: 
     /O.NEW.KPHI.SV.W.0050.130626T2329Z-130627T0015Z/
    It is documented here: http://www.nws.noaa.gov/os/vtec/pdfs/VTEC_explanation6.pdf
    Author:
    pcurtis
